[412.629805, "o", "sing exhaustive search with pruning.\r\n    \r\n    Strategy: Try all key[5] values, and for each, try to find\r\n    a consistent set of other keys using smart search.\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    \r\n    # Collect multiple plaintext-ciphertext pairs\r\n    pairs = []\r\n    for i in range(3):\r\n        pt = i\r\n        ct = encrypt_fn(pt)\r\n        pairs.append((pt, ct))\r\n    \r\n    # Try all key[5] values\r\n    for seed5 in range(0x10000):\r\n        key5 = (seed5 * 1234567) & 0xFFFFFFFF\r\n        \r\n        # For this key[5], try to fi"]
